{"about_the_game":"Day of the Shell is a fast-paced tactical roguelite, where each turn is played in a single click.<br><br>The gods have brought down their wrath on humanity, and only a few remote islands remain. A lonely monster huntress has risen to challenge and appease the gods, traveling through what's left of the world.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008340/extras/2click.gif?t=1737737727\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>One Click, One Turn: Tactical choices are made with <strong>a single click</strong>, making gameplay simple and dynamic while maintaining strategic depth.<br></li><li>Explore the Islands: Survive against monsters and collect treasures on each island to open its portal. Will you be able <strong>to reach the heart of the Islands</strong> and destroy the Shell?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008340/extras/Explore_.gif?t=1737737727\" /><br><br></li><li>Shape Your Destiny: Combine the powers of the many <strong>Warden's blessings</strong> to fight your enemies. Different variations and combinations will allow you to create a unique playstyle for each game.<br></li><li>Death is Part of the Adventure: With each death, you return to your home island, where you can <strong>permanently upgrade</strong> or consider your strategy for the next day.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008340/extras/blessings.gif?t=1737737727\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008340/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737737727","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008340/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737737727","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008340/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737737727","caps